<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10199875>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–2. Habitus of Sinacrulia: 1–S. fortiterpunctata (holotype), 2–S. sp. Scale bars: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10199875/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10199877>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–8. Mouthparts of Sinacrulia fortiterpunctata (holotype): 3–labrum (dorsal view), 4–left mandible (dorsal view), 5–right mandible (dorsal view), 6–labium (ventral view), 7–mentum (ventral view), 8–right maxilla (dorsal view). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10199877/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10199879>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–10. Aedeagus of Sinacrulia fortiterpunctata (holotype): 9–parameral view, 10–lateral view. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10199879/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10199883>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–15. Abdominal segments of Sinacrulia (Figs 11–12: S. fortiterpunctata (holotype), Figs. 13–15: S. sp.): 11–male tergite VIII (dorsal view), 12–male sternite VIII (ventral view), 13–female tergite VIII (dorsal view), 14–female sternite VIII (ventral view), 15–female genital segment (dorsal view). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10199883/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10199887>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Distribution of Sinacrulia in China (black circle: S. fortiterpunctata, white circle: S. sp.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10199887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

